caption.title: Analysis of temporal signal in CHIKV, ZIKV, DENV-2, and MAYV full genome sequence datasets.
caption.p: Plots represent root-to-tip genetic distance in the ML phylogeny versus sampling time for each taxa, (A) CHIKV, (B) ZIKV, (C) DENV-2 and (D) MAYV. The correlation coefficient “r” is reported for each linear regression.
